name: Yudhistira Lost in Space
description:
My second collection from Hinduism Art after Shinta Dance. Yudhistira is one of protagonist in Mahabharata story who plays role as a great king in Amarta. He ever feels like lost in space when he is trapped by his enemy evil plans. The plans put his brothers and wife in deeply sorrow.

The art considered to part of Indonesian Culture Collection, which total consist of 11 edition behalf on The Art Moment Jakarta Event 2021.
